parameters: '怪奇！古生物UMA怪人アノマロカリスモスマン！！の巻'

Shark Broccoli: Great Shark Duke, rejoice... You have
received a challenge from the largest organization in the
city, "Poison Darkness Cambrian".

Memimi: Oh... The famous S-rank monster, "Anomalocaris
Mosman", leads that martial organization. This will be a
true test of our strength!

Shark Broccoli: The upcoming battle will determine the fate
of the city... The leaders of the four major organizations
have agreed to stake their entire organizations on this
fight. The losing side will have their territory,
operations, and members all absorbed by the victor!

Memimi: It's 100 billion trillion million percent
impossible, but if I were to lose, all of us would become
members of the enemy organization. Of course, if we win,
we'll absorb everything from their organization...

Shark Broccoli: I have no doubts about your strength, but
Anomalocaris Mosman is a dangerous monster... He is far
stronger than any enemy you've faced before! Even
Brachiocondor, whom you recently fought, doesn't come close
to his level...

Anomalocaris Mosman: Moooosssss! It's been a while, Shark
Broccoli... I'll be taking your territory, operations, and
the whole organization!

Memimi: Hahaha... Losing territory will be your concern,
won't it? You can only speak so casually to the great boss
Shark Broccoli now... After the Monster Fight is over,
you'll be a low-ranking monster in our organization!

Henchman: Kekeke! This guy thinks he can beat the boss... If
you wet yourself with fear in the ring and regret it, don't
say we didn't warn you!

Henchman: Boss, once we get their organization, let's make
this little girl everyone's errand runner!! Make her wear
more revealing clothes or something... like an all-access
pass for touching...

Memimi: You vulgar lot... With henchmen like you, it's clear
what kind of quality the entire organization has! Words from
such lowly monsters like you aren't even worth getting upset
over!!

Shark Broccoli: Regardless of who wins, in a few days we'll
be comrades in the same organization. Let's save our grudges
for now... I'm looking forward to the day of the match.

Anomalocaris Mosman: Ah, if I hadn't retired from Monster
Fight, I would have truly wanted to battle you! The woman
discovered by Shark Broccoli, once called the strongest
monster... I won't take you lightly!

Memimi: Don't underestimate me... If you don't go all out
from the start, it'll be over in an instant. I plan to fight
with full power from the beginning... You should do the
same!

The tension of a hair-trigger standoff was maintained until
the end as the face-off between the two organizations
concluded...

Memimi: Well then, today is finally the day of the Monster
Fight with Anomalocaris Mosman. Win or lose, our
organization will change significantly... I must get psyched
up!

Memimi: There's plenty of time before the match starts.
Maybe I'll take a little stroll around town...
